<img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1681283 lazyload lazyload" src="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Denola-Grey-Bella-Najia-style-1-479x598.jpg" alt="" width="1280" height="1599" srcset="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Denola-Grey-Bella-Najia-style-1-479x598.jpg 479w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Denola-Grey-Bella-Najia-style-1-922x1152.jpg 922w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Denola-Grey-Bella-Najia-style-1-192x240.jpg 192w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Denola-Grey-Bella-Najia-style-1-384x480.jpg 384w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Denola-Grey-Bella-Najia-style-1-480x600.jpg 480w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Denola-Grey-Bella-Najia-style-1.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /> Becoming the style icon you hope to be is not an easy journey. There are the worry lines that form on your head when deciding what pair of shoes match a shirt, and staying abreast of fashion trends is quite difficult. We know a way to make the process easier. Three words: Instagram fashion influencers. Birthed from the womb of social media is the popular picture-sharing platform called Instagram. This app introduced fashion influencers who provide our feed with drool-worthy pictures. These men, based on their fashion knowledge, provide insights on proper outfit combinations that make us sometimes wonder if they are aliens, representing a distant planet where being fashionable is a norm. Some of the trends in the fashion industry are dictated by influencers. The outfits worn in their pictures could inspire you, serving as a guide in making styling choices. If you wish to step up your style game, here are five Nigerian Instagram fashion influencers for you to check out. When the words “Nigeria, fashion, and men” come to mind, you can’t help but think of Denola Grey. Changing the Nigerian fashion scene for over ten years now, Denola has proven to be a show stopping fashion icon. From his unforgettable AMVCA look to the varieties of ground-breaking and gender non-conforming outfits, we can’t help but stay glued to our phones, anticipating his next picture. <img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1681290 lazyload" src="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Enioluwa-bella-Najia-1-399x598.jpg" alt="Enioluwa-bella-Najia-" width="1280" height="1920" srcset="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Enioluwa-bella-Najia-1-399x598.jpg 399w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Enioluwa-bella-Najia-1-768x1152.jpg 768w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Enioluwa-bella-Najia-1-1024x1536.jpg 1024w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Enioluwa-bella-Najia-1-1366x2048.jpg 1366w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Enioluwa-bella-Najia-1-160x240.jpg 160w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Enioluwa-bella-Najia-1-320x480.jpg 320w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Enioluwa-bella-Najia-1-400x600.jpg 400w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Enioluwa-bella-Najia-1.jpg 1707w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /> When you are not laughing your heart out at his funny rants, you are sure to be obsessed with an outfit in one of his pictures. Popularly referred to as the lipgloss boy, Enioluwa is the literal definition of a star, with his personality radiating through his outfits. Looking for an influencer whose style reflects class and fun? This is your guy. <img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1681286 lazyload" src="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Ebuka-Ghgossip-1-484x598.jpg" alt="Ebuka-Ghgossip" width="1280" height="1581" srcset="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Ebuka-Ghgossip-1-484x598.jpg 484w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Ebuka-Ghgossip-1-933x1152.jpg 933w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Ebuka-Ghgossip-1-194x240.jpg 194w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Ebuka-Ghgossip-1-389x480.jpg 389w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Ebuka-Ghgossip-1-486x600.jpg 486w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Ebuka-Ghgossip-1.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" />  For the next ten years at least, we don’t think anyone is going to forget the agbada Ebuka wore that shook the internet. The agbada became a fashion trend, inspiring various interpretations. Redefining men’s fashion, Ebuka continues to impress his 3.5 million followers with amazing looks that center on being a cool, classy, and stylish man. <img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1681288 lazyload" src="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Akin-Faminu-Bella-Najia-1-478x598.jpg" alt="Akin-Faminu-Bella-Najia-" width="1280" height="1600" srcset="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Akin-Faminu-Bella-Najia-1-478x598.jpg 478w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Akin-Faminu-Bella-Najia-1-922x1152.jpg 922w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Akin-Faminu-Bella-Najia-1-192x240.jpg 192w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Akin-Faminu-Bella-Najia-1-384x480.jpg 384w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Akin-Faminu-Bella-Najia-1-480x600.jpg 480w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Akin-Faminu-Bella-Najia-1.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" />  One might think that with the tight schedule doctors have, their style game will be flat. But Akin proves doctors can have it all. Starting from his days in the university, we watched him fly the fashionista flag high. Wearing incredible outfits and great posing skills, we cannot help but constantly want a glimpse into his world. <img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1681309 lazyload" src="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Prince-Nelson-Enwerem-Twitter-1-478x598.jpg" alt="Prince-Nelson-Enwerem-Twitter-" width="1280" height="1600" srcset="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Prince-Nelson-Enwerem-Twitter-1-478x598.jpg 478w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Prince-Nelson-Enwerem-Twitter-1-922x1152.jpg 922w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Prince-Nelson-Enwerem-Twitter-1-192x240.jpg 192w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Prince-Nelson-Enwerem-Twitter-1-384x480.jpg 384w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Prince-Nelson-Enwerem-Twitter-1-480x600.jpg 480w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Prince-Nelson-Enwerem-Twitter-1.jpg 960w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" />  Ever since his time on a popular reality show, Prince has been pegged as a fashionable man to watch. There is something about his style that makes you want to get your friends and plan a heist for his wardrobe.  With a fresh take on fashion, Prince continues to surprise us with the versatility of his style. Now, we get why his name is “Prince,” because his style screams royalty. Having these influencers’ names, you know what to do. Go out there and seek inspiration. Maybe your name might appear on a list like this one day. I hope you enjoyed reading this article. Thank you.